discord_bot/
├── bot.py               # Main bot entry point
├── config.py            # Loads token, config, etc.
├── .env                 # Contains DISCORD_TOKEN
├── requirements.txt     # Python dependencies
├── cogs/                # Modular bot commands
│   ├── __init__.py
│   ├── base.py          # Simple !ping or hello commands
│   └── odds.py          # Betting-related commands
├── utils/               # Utility functions for DB, blockchain, etc.
│   └── algorand.py
│   └── db.py
└── README.md            # Local dev instructions